# UI demo source webms. The .gif is what the README embeds; the .webm
# is a regeneration-source kept around but not committed because longer
# recordings (e.g. the gcp-pubsub multi-iteration walkthrough at ~2min)
# blow past the 5MB pre-commit large-file guard. Re-record from source
# via `make demo-ui` / `make demo-ui-run`.
docs/demo/*.webm
